data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, nestled in the serene, gated community of Brunswick Plantation. Built in 2022, this modern gem combines contemporary design with unrivaled comfort, offering a lifestyle of elegance and tranquility.As you enter, be greeted by the exquisite  laminate flooring that gracefully unites each space, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. The split-bedroom floor plan ensures privacy and space, making each room a peaceful retreat. Granite countertops adorn the spacious kitchen, offering both beauty and durability, ready to handle your culinary adventures.This home is better than new with all the updates the sellers have made; sliding glass doors, custom screens, new light fixtures, granite less than a month old, new sink and so much more!Each of the four generously sized bedrooms is a haven of comfort, with the first floor master suite boasting an en-suite bathroom and a view of the private, wooded lot. Imagine waking up to the serene views of nature, with a picturesque small pond adding a touch of magic to the landscape.Located in Brunswick Plantation, enjoy exclusive access to a world of amenities. Spend sunny afternoons by the pool, engage in friendly matches at the pickle ball courts, and explore more recreational options that elevate your living experience. There is no shortage of amenities at Brunswick Plantation; golf, indoor/outdoor pool, restaurant, tennis courts and more just to name a few. Privacy is paramount, with the gated community ensuring a secure, peaceful environment for you and your loved ones.Don't miss the opportunity to call this elegant house your home. A blend of modern design, natural beauty, and luxurious amenities awaits. Schedule a viewing today and step into a life of luxury and comfort.
